item.description:

if ur using JDK 6u10
ur classpath should be:

CLASSPATH=C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_10\bin;%CLASSPATH%;

Ur PATH should be:

C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_10\bin
